title: António Vozone
text: António Vozone (born 16 June 1960) is a Portuguese <a href="equestrianism">equestrian</a>. He competed in the <a href="Equestrian%20at%20the%201996%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Individual%20jumping">individual jumping event</a> at the <a href="1996%20Summer%20Olympics">1996 Summer Olympics</a>.
